criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Age group 18-65;

          -  Newly diagnosed smear or GeneXpert positive for TB with or without SARS-CoV-2 (present
             or prior asymptomatic) disease;

          -  Willing to provide written informed consent.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Any prior episode of TB disease;

          -  Treatment for current TB episode >1 week before enrollment;

          -  Drug resistance TB patients;

          -  Pregnancy or childbirth within last 6 months;

          -  Diabetes, HIV-seropositive and current use of immunosuppressive and steroid therapy
             Mild, Moderate and severe Covid-19 disease.
